name: Ego Next Door with Jennifer Hachiya

episodes.title: Coffee and Cults Next Door with Jennifer Hachiya | Hosted by Marilyn Honig
episodes.description:
Join me and Marilyn for a for an interesting, serious, fun, real, interactive chat about cults and narcissism. 

This stream is hosted by Marilyn on her channel Coffee, Cults and Crafts.

Marilyn Honig is a cult/ abuse survivor, crafty SPTV personality, and all-round baddass whose strength and resilience has been put to the test since her very first years on Earth. Honig was also was raised in a strict pentecostal foster home, and later spent 16 years in a Fundamentalist Christian cult. Follow Marilyn's journey @coffeecultsandcrafts  .
